-O2G3aLUZQ_RwRX3oLcr.title: Individual Assessment - The Sorting Hat
-O2G3aLUZQ_RwRX3oLcr.description: This is my first individual student assessment for Nashville Software School, which is the Sorting Hat project. The project has a welcome page, function such as entering a name, sorting into houses, and filtering the results. There is also a randomization feature and and option to expel a student.

-O2G3aLVVHUcdV6nDe6n.title: Individual Assessment - Team Roster
-O2G3aLVVHUcdV6nDe6n.description: An individual assessment front-end project. Site built using React/Next.js. A team roster app with full CRUD capability, API fetch calls, search functionality, styled using Bootstrap & custom CSS.

-O2G3aLW1k7NcGX7k72l.title: Front-end Capstone Project - Restaurant Roamer
-O2G3aLW1k7NcGX7k72l.description:
My FE Capstone project: Restaurant Roamer - the restaurant tracking app we have all been waiting for.
Learned several new things with this project including implementing an external API and using Daisy UI.
Tech Stack:
- CSS
- JavaScript
- React/Next.js
- Daisy UI
- Google Places API
- Firebase
- Netlify

App Features:
- Explore a database of restaurants
- Track restaurants on your Eat List
- Utilize the “Suggest a Restaurant” feature
- Full CRUD functionality
- Favorites

-O2G3aLW1k7NcGX7k722.title: Hackathon Project - Podcast Player
-O2G3aLW1k7NcGX7k722.description:
My team's creation from the Nashville Software School Hackathon: Soundscape - the ultimate podcast playlist creator app! 
Ever struggled to curate the perfect playlist for your mood? Say hello to Soundscape! With our app, you can seamlessly craft personalized podcast playlists tailored to your interests, moods, and activities. 
Here's what Soundscape brings to the table:
Intuitive Interface: User-friendly design for effortless navigation. 
Customizable 
Playlists: Mix, match, and organize podcasts to suit your preferences.
Favorites: Favorite your top podcasts and/or playlists.

-O2G3aLW1k7NcGX7k723.title: Group Project - Hip Hop, Pizza, and Wangs
-O2G3aLW1k7NcGX7k723.description: Worked with Nashville Software School teammates on our group project to build a web solution for a mom and pop restaurant called Hip Hop, Pizza, and Wangs.

-O2G3aLW1k7NcGX7k724.title: Individual Assessment - Vocab-YOU-lary
-O2G3aLW1k7NcGX7k724.description: This app is a vocabulary card repository that allows you to create vocab cards including details such as the term, definition, and category. The app has full CRUD capabilities.
